trans-unit.source: Specifies the type of change occurring in a collection of <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: コレクションで発生している変更の種類を指定<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>オブジェクト。

trans-unit.source: The DesignerActionListsChangedType enumeration indicates that an element has been added or removed from a managed collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects.
trans-unit.target: DesignerActionListsChangedType 列挙体は、要素が追加または管理対象のコレクションから削除されていることを示します<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>オブジェクト。</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> 。

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used in the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs> class, which is associated with the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged> event.
trans-unit.target: この列挙体で使用、<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>と関連付けられているクラス、<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>イベント</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged></xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListsChangedEventArgs>。

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > Although the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection> class is a collection of <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList> objects, it does not directly raise events.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > ですが、<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>クラスは、コレクションの<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList>オブジェクト、イベントを直接発生しません</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList></xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionListCollection>。

代わりに、所有している<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService>を発生させます<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged>イベント</xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService.DesignerActionListsChanged></xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionService>。

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been added to the collection.
trans-unit.target: 1 つまたは複数<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>オブジェクトがコレクションに追加します。

trans-unit.source: One or more <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref> objects have been removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: 1 つまたは複数<xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.DesignerActionList"></xref>コレクションから削除されたオブジェクト。
